00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:18,000
The goal of the company is to be kind of an enabler to evaluate the possibility of creating the first hydrogen society in the world here in Iceland.

619
00:52:18,000 --> 00:52:25,000
They foresaw Iceland as a perfect test ground because they knew that all the energy sources to produce the hydrogen would be or renewable,

620
00:52:25,000 --> 00:52:27,000
coming from hydro or geothermal.

621
00:52:27,000 --> 00:52:30,000
This ship is of course mainly a touristic boat, whale watching.

